### 测试1：新增学生（正常情况，Service校验通过）
POST http://localhost:8080/student/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "42411169",
  "name": "蒋沛珍",
  "className": "计算机科学与技术2班"
}

### 测试2：新增学生（学号为空，触发Service校验，课件要求的业务校验）
POST http://localhost:8080/student/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "",
  "name": "蒋沛珍",
  "className": "计算机科学与技术2班"
}

