GET http://localhost:8080/student/42411169

### 测试：新增用户
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "测试学生1",
  "role": "student"
}

### 测试：更新用户
PUT http://localhost:8080/user/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3,
  "password": "654321",
  "realName": "测试学生1-更新",
  "role": "teacher"
}

### 测试：删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/user/delete/3

### 测试：新增用户（绝对不重复的用户名）
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan002",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "张三测试",
  "role": "student"
}

### 测试：新增用户（JPA自动生成INSERT SQL）
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jpa_test001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "JPA测试用户",
  "role": "student"
}

### 测试：更新用户（JPA自动生成UPDATE SQL）
PUT http://localhost:8080/user/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 6,
  "password": "654321",
  "realName": "JPA测试用户-更新",
  "role": "teacher"
}

### 测试：删除用户（JPA自动生成DELETE SQL）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/user/delete/6

